snippet.textDisplay: Brilliant song by Anuv.... I am in the love of the lyrics. For me this lyrics really creates a very abstract image for me and i love that. The whole song production is amazing. A special mention of Sarthak Kalyani who has sung a sargam in this song. Sarthak is a brilliant singer, i love his voice and the way he render sargam in this song. This is the true sign of a good singer where Sarthak  had only sung the sargam for few seconds but as a singer he made an impact to the song. I was immediately able to recognise sarthak's voice as i am a big fan of him from Arrived days. All the best to the whole team.
